The paper deals with a method for filtering dynamic population codes, which involves machine learning and optimization techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with control systems and information theory, which suggests cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.IT (Information Theory) as possible sub-categories.
